{"tid":2200254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"輿論機器傷口灑鹽 馮煒光質疑家屬身份真偽 斥為政治「消費家人」","createTime":"2020-09-12T19:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T04:41:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4848721cae028bd390ae65d1967bdc544ef708","tid":2200254,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T19:41:56.000Z","msg":"6名被捕人士家屬周六（12日）在記招上憂心忡忡，不住拭淚，只求得知至親是否尚在人間。建制輿論機器已啟動，抹黑記招上以black bloc、戴口罩的家屬「身份可疑」。前新聞統籌專員馮煒光即日更於黨媒《文匯報》撰文，質疑記招「不遺餘力地抺黑內地」、打國際戰綫，更稱：「倘若這批是真家屬，只能說他們是被反對派利用了，消費了！」<br />\n<br />\n文中一開首，馮煒光自稱由「公關角度」看，稱選擇這個時候開記者會是「非常錯的時機」，予內地官方及民眾「有人借機打國際戰綫」之感。馮舉例指記者第一條問題便是用英文問到「國際社會」，會上其中一位協助家屬的「煽暴派成員」鄒家成更「赤裸裸地要求國際社會關注中國的人權律師狀況」；就連涂謹申「一開口是先說英文」，馮亦指為「向蓬佩奧放話」。<br />\n<br />\n馮又舉例指，會上另一「煽暴派議員」朱凱廸多次提到「國際社會」及「中國律師」境況，「不遺餘力地抺黑內地」。馮指：「倘若這批是真家屬，只能說他們是被反對派利用了，消費了！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/YESKMLXQU5CJJGM7DJ6MPCD7L4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FYESKMLXQU5CJJGM7DJ6MPCD7L4%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Sbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=2120e3ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FYESKMLXQU5CJJGM7DJ6MPCD7L4%2F&h=8f13658f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/YESKMLXQU5CJJGM7DJ6MPCD7L4/</a>"},{"pid":"9130cd40da9eaee8db0aeebaf88425dc183b1766","tid":2200254,"uid":201359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T19:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad6f3ecf088ea62357c20a796ba3bf394bf646a","tid":2200254,"uid":273703,"like":11,"